snippet.title: Hyper Jam | Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Hyper Jam is a neon-soaked arena brawler full of lethal weapons, stackable perks, furious combat, and a killer synthwave soundtrack. Coming to PS4, Xbox One and Steam on 12 February, 2019!

Wishlist on Steam! 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/556050/Hyper_Jam/

Join the Discord! 
https://hyperjamgame.com/discord

Find out more!
https://hyperjamgame.com
